erience.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an account\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"your reading experience\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 54% of the votes cast in the low-turnout election supported the measure to triple parking fees for large SUV drivers from out of town to 18 euros ($19.50) per hour in the city's center, according to official results from City Hall.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than 54%\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"the votes\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the low-turnout election\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the measure\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"triple parking fees\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"large SUV drivers\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"18 euros\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"hour\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 888}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's center\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"official results\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"City Hall\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only 5.7% of the 1.3 million eligible voters cast ballots at the 39 voting stations around the city.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only 5.7%\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1.3 million eligible voters\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"ballots\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"the 39 voting stations\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In get-out-the-vote posts on social media, Hidalgo argued that SUVs take up too much space on narrow Parisian streets, are too polluting and \\\"threaten our health and our planet,\\\" and cause more traffic accidents than smaller cars.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999987586842026, \"rank\": 1.241317198804557e-06, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the-vote\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"SUVs\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"too much space\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"narrow Parisian streets\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"our health\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"our planet\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"more traffic accidents\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"smaller cars\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The additional fees will come into force from Sept. 1, Hidalgo said.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999987586842026, \"rank\": 1.241317198804557e-06, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The additional fees\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"force\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"Sept.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get the latest headlines, breaking news and columns.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the latest headlines\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"columns\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By signing up you consent to receive the above newsletter from Postmedia Network Inc. A welcome email is on its way.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Postmedia Network Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Postmedia_Network\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the above newsletter\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1471}, {\"ngram\": \"A welcome email\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"its way\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not see it, please check your junk folder.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your junk folder\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next issue of Top Stories will soon be in your inbox.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The next issue\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"Top Stories\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We encountered an issue signing you up.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an issue\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please try again Interested in more newsletters?Browse here.\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more newsletters?Browse\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The time has come to break with this tendency for cars that are always bigger, taller, wider,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The time\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"this tendency\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have the power to take back ownership of our streets.\\\"\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"ownership\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"our streets\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cost for non-residents to park SUVs in Paris' central districts, in the arrondissements numbered 1 through 11, would soar to 18 euros ($19.5) per hour for the first two hours, compared to 6 euros per hour for smaller cars.\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1958, \"end\": 1963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1400947345990793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cost\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"non\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"SUVs\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"the arrondissements\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"18 euros\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"hour\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"the first two hours\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"6 euros\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"hour\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"smaller cars\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After that, parking would become increasingly punitive.\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parking\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A six-hour stay with an SUV - enough, say, to take in a show and a restaurant - would cost a whopping 225 euros ($243), compared to 75 euros for smaller vehicles.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A six-hour stay\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"an SUV\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"a show\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"a restaurant\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"a whopping 225 euros\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"75 euros\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"smaller vehicles\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Away from the heart of the city, in Paris' outer arrondissements numbered 12 through 20, an out-of-town SUV driver would pay 12 euros per hour for the first two hours, progressively rising to 150 euros for six hours.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1400947345990793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"12 euros\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"hour\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"the first two hours\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"150 euros\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"six hours\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mini-referendum was open to Parisians registered to vote.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The mini\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"referendum\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The question they were asked was: \\\"For or against the creation of a specific rate for the parking of heavy, bulky, polluting individual cars?\\\"\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The question\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific rate\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"the parking\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"individual cars\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cyreane Demur, a 20-year-old student, voted in the chic 8th arrondissement that includes that car-clogged Champs-Elysees boulevard and its chaotic traffic circle around the monumental Arc de Triomphe.\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9992163039517089, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elysees\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}, {\"begin\": 2971, \"end\": 2986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2437158839725225e-18, \"text\": \"Arc de Triomphe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cyreane Demur\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"a 20-year-old student\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"the chic 8th arrondissement\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"its chaotic traffic circle\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Demur said heavier cars make congestion \\\"even more complicated\\\" and that \\\"one must consider the ecology, the parking issues.\\\"\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Demur\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"heavier cars\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"congestion\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3066}, {\"ngram\": \"the ecology\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3092}, {\"ngram\": \"the parking issues\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Jadine L'Orlendu, a 75-year-old voter, said SUVs \\\"do not disturb me, they do not take more space than other cars, the parking places are marked, and people should drive what they want to drive.\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jadine L'Orlendu\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3136}, {\"ngram\": \"a 75-year-old voter\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"SUVs\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"more space\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"other cars\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3232}, {\"ngram\": \"the parking places\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about freedom.\\\"\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 3325, \"to\": 3332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vote follows another City Hall consultation last year on whether to ban for-hire electric scooters.\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vote\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"another City Hall consultation\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"for-hire electric scooters\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 15,000 opinion-dividing mini-machines were subsequently banished from Paris streets after nearly 90% of the 103,000 voters rejected e-scooters.\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3514, \"end\": 3519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1400947345990793e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http